                        <p class="- topic/p ">
                           <b otherprops="generalM" class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Only for
systems with manual bypass switches: </b>
                           <xref href="#./BP_SetManualBypassSwitchesToAuto-AA6C103D"
