                                 type="section"
                                 class="- topic/xref "/>.</p>
                     </li>
                  </ol>
               </li>
               <li class="- topic/li ">
                  <p class="- topic/p ">After both units are checked and in normal operation, continue
with the section <xref href="Bruce_Connecting_the_Output_Distribution_CPT_0000916515.dita"
